Einstein Report Formula Generation Error Messages

If Einstein’s response doesn’t meet your expectations, you can generate another response by entering a new request. On the other hand, if your request doesn’t provide the information needed, Einstein lets you know.

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Lightning Experience.
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions with Einstein 1 Sales Edition and Einstein 1 Service Edition.

Einstein Report Formula Generation Error Messages

COMMON ERROR MESSAGES
I couldn't find the field and function combination that matches your request. Try describing the calculation using different words. 
Einstein couldn’t match your words with fields or functions needed to build a formula.
It looks like you want to apply the [X] function to the [Y] field, but that's a [Z type] field. Try your request again, but use different words to describe the field and function combination. 
I couldn't generate a formula. Try describing the calculation using different words. 
I can't complete your request because you reached the character limit. Shorten your request and try again. 
I couldn’t understand your request. Describe a calculation related to the report. 
Something went wrong. Change your request and try again. 
Something went wrong. Try again.
